WEBVTT

00:04:00.240 --> 00:04:02.336
She had forgotten
to make that clear earlier

00:04:02.360 --> 00:04:04.218
because she assumed it was ... obvious.

00:04:04.242 --> 00:04:06.296
(Laughter)

00:04:06.320 --> 00:04:09.096
A boy had the second highest
score on the test,

00:04:09.120 --> 00:04:11.160
and he would be monitor.

00:04:11.960 --> 00:04:14.136
Now, what was even more
interesting about this

00:04:14.160 --> 00:04:17.976
is that the boy was a sweet, gentle soul

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:20.959
who had no interest
in patrolling the class with the cane,

00:04:22.120 --> 00:04:25.320
while I was full of ambition to do so.

00:04:26.560 --> 00:04:28.656
But I was female and he was male,

00:04:28.680 --> 00:04:30.347
and so he became the class monitor.